data.title: Another Safety Notice for the ACUSON SC2000, Siemens
data.meta_description: Siemens issued a Field Safety Notice concerning a potential unsafe mechanical condition with the ACUSON SC2000 ultrasound system with serial numbers 401100 to 401400. Corrective actions are planned.
